lead_paragraph: Greg Monroe had 19 points and 10 rebounds to help the Milwaukee Bucks overcome O.J. Mayo's wild ejection in a 95-85 victory over the Minnesota Timberwolves on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Bucks Shake Off Mayo's Ejection to Beat Timberwolves 95-85
